    "body": "### Topic\n\nmetrics datadog\n\n### Relevant information\n\nHi,\nWe are deploying Airbyte using Helm and it seems that datadog metrics are not published anymore starting with the version `1.5.0`.\nI saw that the [OpenTelemetry (OTel) metrics monitoring feature introduced in version `1.5.0`](https://github.com/airbytehq/airbyte/releases/tag/v1.5.0) is specifically labeled as a Self-Managed Enterprise feature. Is datadog metrics monitoring also only available as an enterprise feature starting with version 1.5 or is it just a bad configuration from our side?",
